title: 12 Stress Management Techniques You Might Not Have Tried
description: In this ideas booklet you will see 12 stress management techniques you might not have tried before. These techniques have the potential to lower your stress quickly.The good news is that this ideas booklet is short but a good starting point to explore techniques that will work for you so you can implement them quickly and get results. It will also make you think about other possibilities because it gives you visuals and the power of images to the mind is very strong.
author: Paulineh James
